text: Al Sarraj or El Sarraj () is an Arabic surname. Notable people with this surname include: * Abdel Hamid Sarraj (1925–2013), Syrian soldier * Eyad El- Sarraj (1944–2013), Palestinian psychiatrist * Fayez al-Sarraj (born 1960), Libyan politician * Mohammad Alsarraj (born 1998), Jordanian squash player
title: Al Sarraj
